&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to partner closely with enterprise sales teams to build and execute impactful programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of enterprise sales cycles, account-based marketing, and field marketing best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to work in a fast-paced, high-growth environment with minimal oversight.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent project management skills; able to run multiple programs concurrently while meeting deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and relationship-building skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
